1
00:00:48,560 --> 00:00:49,420
Your Highness.

2
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:50,860
Your Highness.

3
00:00:52,720 --> 00:00:54,360
I beg Your Highness to release the little prince.

4
00:00:54,360 --> 00:00:55,160
How impudent!

5
00:00:55,600 --> 00:00:57,600
A mere servant dares to block my way.

6
00:00:59,080 --> 00:01:00,680
You are just a lowly servant,

7
00:01:01,080 --> 00:01:03,080
yet you think so highly of yourself.

8
00:01:03,680 --> 00:01:06,010
If I am willing to be punished in his place,

9
00:01:06,880 --> 00:01:09,480
will Your Highness release the little prince?

10
00:01:15,960 --> 00:01:16,520
Oh.

11
00:01:17,360 --> 00:01:19,400
I never noticed it before.

12
00:01:19,960 --> 00:01:23,160
You are quite a handsome one.

13
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:26,120
Do you really like being beaten?

14
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:29,000
Hahaha.

15
00:01:29,720 --> 00:01:30,640
Alright.

16
00:01:31,480 --> 00:01:34,600
If you can endure 81 lashes,

17
00:01:35,600 --> 00:01:36,479
then I

18
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:39,460
will let you take the little prince back.

19
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:41,330
I hope Your Highness

20
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:43,600
keeps your word.

21
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:44,720
Men,

22
00:01:45,600 --> 00:01:47,280
beat him mercilessly.

23
00:01:54,479 --> 00:01:56,340
If we fail to rescue Consort Rong,

24
00:01:56,880 --> 00:01:57,940
Jingyuan might...

25
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:12,160
Report!

26
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,600
Your Majesty, I intercepted

27
00:02:15,600 --> 00:02:17,520
the carriage the Grand Princess used to transfer Consort Rong.

28
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:19,000
I don't know what torture she suffered,

29
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:21,000
but she kept babbling about witchcraft and dark arts.

30
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:23,040
Fortunately, seeing her suffer so much,

31
00:02:23,040 --> 00:02:24,640
Consort Rong has confessed.

32
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:28,240
This must be her usual trick.

33
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:30,610
Prepare a carriage.

34
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:31,640
Go to the Grand Princess's estate.

35
00:02:31,640 --> 00:02:32,000
Yes.

36
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:33,079
Wait.

37
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:36,480
The ministers are impeaching you and A Yan right now.

38
00:02:36,480 --> 00:02:37,610
You should stay here

39
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:39,800
and stall the ministers.

40
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:40,960
And I.

41
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:43,800
I will go to the Grand Princess's mansion right now.

42
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:45,880
And use the evidence to shut them up.

43
00:02:48,920 --> 00:02:52,000
Sixty, sixty-one.

44
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:55,680
Sixty-two, sixty-three.

45
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,200
Stop.

46
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:29,920
Oh,

47
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:33,240
my mansion is quite lively today.

48
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:36,840
Eunuchs and maids are coming in swarms.

49
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,240
Speak.

50
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:39,880
What is it?

51
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:43,320
Everyone in the Princess's estate, hear my order.

52
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:50,200
By the mandate of Heaven, the Emperor decrees:

53
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:53,600
Regarding the rumors of an illicit affair between Prince Rui and Consort Rong,

54
00:03:53,600 --> 00:03:55,600
I have personally overseen a thorough investigation

55
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:57,240
and finally uncovered the truth.

56
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:58,720
Prince Rui was wrongly accused

57
00:03:58,720 --> 00:03:59,880
and framed.

58
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:02,250
Therefore, I issue this decree

59
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:04,050
to set the record straight.

60
00:04:04,440 --> 00:04:05,520
Respect this.

61
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:09,320
His Majesty is truly interesting.

62
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:11,920
Yesterday he took Consort Rong for interrogation.

63
00:04:11,920 --> 00:04:13,640
Today, without any evidence,

64
00:04:14,200 --> 00:04:16,399
a decree has arrived instead.

65
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:19,880
It seems His Majesty wants to use an imperial decree

66
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:22,800
to suppress me, his aunt.

67
00:04:23,280 --> 00:04:24,940
Who said there's no evidence?

68
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:25,800
How dare you!

69
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:32,400
This concerns the dignity of the royal family.

70
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:35,280
How could a mere imperial edict brush it off?

71
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:40,480
If Consort Rong hadn't confessed in front of me personally,

72
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:42,080
I wouldn't have believed it.

73
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:45,320
Consort Rong.

74
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:47,400
Tell us everything you know.

75
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:49,600
I...

76
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:56,080
Consort Rong.

77
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:00,200
Don't be nervous.

78
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:01,800
I'm here.

79
00:05:04,400 --> 00:05:06,920
It was me who wanted to play games with the young prince.

80
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:08,320
While he was asleep,

81
00:05:08,320 --> 00:05:10,400
I secretly climbed into his bed.

82
00:05:10,400 --> 00:05:12,200
This has nothing to do with him.

83
00:05:12,200 --> 00:05:14,840
I'm willing to bear all the blame alone.

84
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:17,120
That's not what you said yesterday.

85
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:21,840
Consort Rong.

86
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:35,200
Alright.

87
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:38,320
The truth has now come to light.

88
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:41,840
So you can just take A'yan back.

89
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:45,120
I am not an unreasonable person.

90
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:49,120
Si Xinglan receives the decree.

91
00:06:04,440 --> 00:06:06,040
Si Xingxuan.

92
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:08,280
Experience counts.

93
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:12,200
You disobey and insist on fighting me.

94
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:15,440
So don't blame me for showing no mercy.

95
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:20,040
Yuanyuan is so good.

96
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:22,320
Why did Auntie hit Yuanyuan?

97
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:24,080
She didn't hit me.

98
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:26,880
I fell down by accident.

99
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:28,880
Really?

100
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:30,600
Yes.

101
00:06:31,400 --> 00:06:32,480
That's good.

102
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:35,240
Auntie didn't hit Ayan.

103
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:38,400
So she probably wouldn't hit Yuanyuan either.

104
00:06:39,200 --> 00:06:40,680
If they dare to hit you,

105
00:06:41,880 --> 00:06:43,480
I will kill them all.

106
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:45,320
Ah?

107
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:47,240
Just kidding.

108
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:51,680
Yuanyuan is telling stories again.

109
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,040
Right, Yuanyuan.

110
00:06:54,280 --> 00:06:56,280
Before Auntie took Ayan away,

111
00:06:56,280 --> 00:06:59,000
you were telling Ayan an unfinished story.

112
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:01,200
Can you tell it to Ayan again?

113
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:04,880
What story?

114
00:07:05,520 --> 00:07:09,240
The older brother was Qin Yuan.

115
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:11,200
And the younger brother was Qin Yan.

116
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:12,520
They were orphans.

117
00:07:12,520 --> 00:07:13,780
They grew up together.

118
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:15,160
Uh, the younger brother

119
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:17,880
went to buy candied fruits for his injured brother.

120
00:07:17,880 --> 00:07:19,600
And then? What happened next?

121
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:21,080
And then...

122
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:26,000
On his way back with the candied fruits...

123
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,320
Candied fruits. Right.

124
00:07:32,320 --> 00:07:34,520
Whenever Ayan felt sick before,

125
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:36,520
Ayan would feel better after eating them.

126
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:38,400
I'll go get some for Yuanyuan.

127
00:07:49,400 --> 00:07:52,680
No one is allowed to break the rules of the game's virtual space.

128
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:55,520
Jingyuan, you broke the rules.

129
00:07:58,240 --> 00:08:00,080
It's you.

130
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:04,200
Don't you know the project manager cannot interfere with the project?

131
00:08:04,200 --> 00:08:05,080
What are you doing?

132
00:08:05,080 --> 00:08:07,920
We agreed to let you into the project.

133
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:09,800
It was so you could accompany your deceased brother.

134
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:12,400
You cannot interfere with the main storyline.

135
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:15,680
But your storylines interfered with Ayan.

136
00:08:16,080 --> 00:08:17,400
Si Xingyan is just

137
00:08:17,400 --> 00:08:19,840
a data construct that looks like your brother.

138
00:08:19,840 --> 00:08:22,200
It's not worth ruining your future for him.

139
00:08:22,200 --> 00:08:24,060
You are destroying this project.

140
00:08:24,440 --> 00:08:26,800
Perhaps when I created him,

141
00:08:28,840 --> 00:08:30,600
he was already no longer just a data construct.

142
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:32,460
How could you have such a thought?

143
00:08:32,919 --> 00:08:35,799
You were the most promising engineer.

144
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:38,460
How can you immerse yourself in a virtual world?

145
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:43,679
I... I said

146
00:08:43,799 --> 00:08:45,600
I would give you three warnings.

147
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:46,880
If you do it again,

148
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:48,840
we will take necessary measures

149
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:51,170
to force you to quit the project and leave.

150
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,200
I disagree.

151
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:54,400
This isn't about whether you agree or not.

152
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:55,880
It's settled then.
